title: Jay Shetty / Mental Health Awareness
description: Heckler? They hardly know her! Priyanka shares her experiences being heckled at her stand-up shows. Jay Shetty joins the podcast to talk about the importance of mental health for Mental Health Awareness Month. Sean asks Jay for tips on practicing mindfulness.
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
